  "body": "Currently go-ethereum blocks 0 gasprice transaction to be saved on txpool and it is different compared with parity node.\r\n\r\n( Here is my edit to enable 0 gasprice transactions to be sended and mined by pool node on other chain when the block is empty https://github.com/eosclassic/eosclassic/commit/90af9e7a6a6e9d8d5b998f7cdaabb8e391336cb5 )\r\n\r\nI would like to suggest enabling 0 gasprice transaction to be accepted by default, we can mine the low fee transaction when the block is empty enough.\r\n\r\n",
